OL,6,FCold weather payments have been paid
OL,7,Fto nearly 1.5 million households
OL,8,Facross England and Wales so far this
OL,9,Fwinter, the Government has said.
OL,11,FThe #25 payments go to low-income
OL,12,Fhouseholds to help them with their
OL,13,Fbills.
OL,15,FCold weather payments are made
OL,16,Fautomatically when temperatures drop
OL,17,Fto 0C or below for seven consecutive
OL,18,Fdays.
