OL,6,FPeople receiving pension credit
OL,7,Fautomatically qualify for the
OL,8,Fpayments, but some households
OL,9,Freceiving other support ` including
OL,10,Funiversal credit and income support `
OL,11,Fmay also be eligible if they meet
OL,12,Fadditional criteria.
OL,14,FSecretary of State for Work and
OL,15,FPensions Pat McFadden said: "This
OL,16,Fsupport is a lifeline for vulnerable
OL,17,Fhouseholds when temperatures plummet."
