OL,6,FMorgan Vine, director of policy and
OL,7,Finfluencing at Independent Age said:
OL,8,F"With more than half of older people
OL,9,Fon low incomes across England and
OL,10,FWales regularly sharing that they are
OL,11,Fworried about meeting the cost of
OL,12,Ftheir heating bill, it is crucial that
OL,13,Fvital support like this reaches those
OL,14,Fwho need it most."
OL,16,FAge UK is encouraging older people on
OL,17,Flow and modest incomes to check if
OL,18,Fthey could claim pension credit, as
OL,19,Fpart of its crisis hiding in plain
OL,20,Fsight campaign.
