OL,6,F"Increases in energy, food and rent
OL,7,Fhave significantly impacted people's
OL,8,Fstandard of living, and after four
OL,9,Fyears we're still hearing harrowing
OL,10,Fstories about older people who are
OL,11,Ftaking drastic measures to get by.
OL,13,F"For those who rely on the state
OL,14,Fpension as their main source of
OL,15,Fincome, pension credit can make a real
OL,16,Fdifference.
OL,18,F"We urge anyone who is watching the
OL,19,Fpennies or cutting back on other daily
OL,20,Fessentials to reach out to Age UK and
OL,21,Fsee what help may be available."
